        "title": "各类发货模式时效要求",
        "severity": "info",
        "severityText": "参考",
        "date": "2025-09-29",
        "tags": [
          "发货时限",
          "QIC仓"
        ],
        "link": "https://school.jinritemai.com/doudian/web/article/101706",
        "body": "<ul><li><span class=\"highlight\">极速发货</span>：当日<span class=\"num\">16:00</span>前付款订单当日<span class=\"num\">23:59:59</span>前发货；<span class=\"num\">16:00</span>后付款次日<span class=\"num\">23:59:59</span>前发货。</li><li><span class=\"highlight\">次日发货</span>：消费者付款后次日<span class=\"num\">23:59:59</span>前发货。</li><li><span class=\"highlight\">QIC仓</span>普通商品：线下送仓<span class=\"num\">48</span>小时内到仓；快递送仓<span class=\"num\">48</span>小时内揽收。</li><li>QIC仓定制/预售类：按承诺时效送仓；质检驳回重新送仓普通<span class=\"num\">48</span>小时，定制<span class=\"num\">120</span>小时。</li></ul>"
